<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Beltline </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">Beltline boasts of a fabulous location and an endless array of things to do. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located to the immediate south of the city downtown, the community is bound by the Elbow
                River on the
                east, the 14th Street W on the west and the 17th Avenue on the south.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">One of the most densely populated neighborhoods in the city of Calgary, the community in
                Calgary is highly urbanized and perfect for young and vibrant professionals and growing families. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Beltline District consists of 4 neighbourhoods West Connaught, Connaught Centre,
                Victoria Crossing
                Centre and East Victoria Crossing. </p>
        </div>
